UBCS map pack
------------------
This is a map pack by TRIX.  In this map pack, there are 3 maps that he made.  All these maps are featured under the zm mod.

zm_ubcs_2_houses
This is another map by TRIX.
This is a simple 2 sided map that has
2 houses as they main buildings.  There 
are about 40 spawns in this map.
========================
zm_ubcs_bank
This is another map by TRIX.  The map
is set in a small bank with small vents, allowed
on roof access, and small rooms.
======================== 
zm_ubcs_maze 
This is another map by TRIX.  This map is 
set in a small maze with a bunch of dead ends.
There are vending machines that you can use to block.
